```
public static Metadata extractMetadatatUsingFacade(InputStream stream) 
  throws IOException, TikaException {
    Tika tika = new Tika();
    Metadata metadata = new Metadata();
 
    tika.parse(stream, metadata);
    return metadata;
}
```


